---
title: Community
---

<div class="community-hero content-block content-block-xl position-relative text-center">
  <div class="container container-md">
    <h1 class="title">You’re going to <%= inline_svg("icons/heart-big.svg", class: "isvg heart")%> this.</h1>
    <p class="lead mb-6">Solidus is an open source ecommerce solution built with Ruby on Rails and maintained by a community of passionate developers.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="d-md-flex justify-content-around">
      <div class="community-content">
        <h2 class="title">5400+</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
          Core commits since 2015
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="community-content">
        <h2 class="title">2000+</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
          Slack channel members
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="community-content">
        <h2 class="title">35</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
          Community-supported extensions
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="community-content">
        <h2 class="title">650+</h2>
        <p>
          Contributors
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="dev-slider">
    <div class="dev-slider-content">
      <img class="img-fluid" src="<%= image_path('illustrations/dev-slider-bg.svg') %>" alt="Solidus community">
      <div class="dev-slide wrapper-1">
        <div class="dev-circle dev-1"></div>
        <div class="dev-circle dev-2"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="dev-slide wrapper-2">
        <div class="dev-circle dev-1"></div>
        <div class="dev-circle dev-2"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="dev-slide wrapper-3">
        <div class="dev-circle dev-1"></div>
        <div class="dev-circle dev-2"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="community-block content-block text-center" data-aos="fade">
  <div class="container container-md mb-6">
    <h2 class="title text-white">Join the Solidus Community.</h2>
    <p class="lead text-white-072">Connect and engage with a worldwide community of Solidus developers, stakeholders  and experts all around the world.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="d-lg-flex justify-content-around">
      <div class="community-content d-flex align-items-center">
        <div class="picture text-center pr-2">
          <div class="card rounded-circle">
            <div class="mx-auto w-100 align-self-center">
              <a href="http://slack.solidus.io/" target="_blank"><%= inline_svg("social-icons/slack-colored.svg", class: "isvg") %></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="description text-left pr-lg-2">
          <h4 class="title text-white">
            Join our Slack
          </h4>
          <p class="text-white-072">
            Connect and chat with other Solidus devs
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="community-content d-flex align-items-center">
        <div class="picture text-center pr-2">
          <div class="card rounded-circle">
            <div class="mx-auto w-100 align-self-center">
              <a href="https://opencollective.com/solidus" target="_blank"><%= inline_svg("social-icons/opencollective-colored.svg", class: "isvg") %></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="description text-left pr-lg-2">
          <h4 class="title text-white">
            Become a donor
          </h4>
          <p class="text-white-072">
            Support this project on Open Collective
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="community-content d-flex align-items-center">
        <div class="picture text-center pr-2">
          <div class="card rounded-circle">
            <div class="mx-auto w-100 align-self-center">
              <a href="https://github.com/solidusio/solidus" target="_blank"><%= inline_svg("social-icons/github-colored.svg", class: "isvg") %></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="description text-left pr-lg-2">
          <h4 class="title text-white">
            GitHub
          </h4>
          <p class="text-white-072">
            Official Solidus GitHub repository
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="community-content d-flex align-items-center">
        <div class="picture text-center pr-2">
          <div class="card rounded-circle">
            <div class="mx-auto w-100 align-self-center">
              <a href="https://guides.solidus.io/developers/" target="_blank"><%= inline_svg("icons/guide.svg", class: "isvg") %></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="description text-left pr-lg-2">
          <h4 class="title text-white">
            Solidus Guide
          </h4>
          <p class="text-white-072">
            Learn the Solidus ecommerce platform
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-block content-block-gray-100" id="core-team" data-aos="fade">
  <div class="container container-md text-center mb-8">
    <h2 class="title">Meet the core team.</h2>
    <p>
      The development of Solidus and its ecosystem is guided by an international team, some of whom have chosen to be featured below.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="container container-lg">
    <div class="bio-block">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md">
          <div class="card card-border-none">
            <div class="photo">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="<%= image_path('team/clarke-brunsdon.png') %>" srcset="<%= image_path('team/clarke-brunsdon.png') %>, <%= image_path('team/clarke-brunsdon@2x.png') %> 2x" alt="Clarke Brunsdon">
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="name">Clarke Brunsdon</h3>
              <p>Senior Director <br> JUUL Labs</p>
              <ul class="links list-unstyled">
                <li>
                  <a href="https://github.com/cbrunsdon" target="_blank"><%= inline_svg("social-icons/github.svg", class: "isvg") %> <strong>cbrunsdon</strong></a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="data col-md">
          <h6 class="text-gray-048">Notable contribution</h6>
          <p>One of the leaders in the decision to fork from Spree.</p>
          <h6 class="text-gray-048">Fun fact</h6>
          <p>Avid Cookie Clicker, poker player, and owner of a cute corgi puppy named Riker.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bio-block">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md">
          <div class="card card-border-none">
            <div class="photo">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="<%= image_path('team/alberto-vena.png') %>" srcset="<%= image_path('team/alberto-vena.png') %>, <%= image_path('team/alberto-vena@2x.png') %> 2x" alt="Alberto Vena">
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="name">Alberto Vena</h3>
              <p>Co-Founder & Developer <br> Nebulab</p>
              <ul class="links list-unstyled">
                <li>
                  <a href="https://github.com/kennyadsl" target="_blank"><%= inline_svg("social-icons/github.svg", class: "isvg") %> <strong>kennyadsl</strong></a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="data col-md">
          <h6 class="text-gray-048">Notable contribution</h6>
          <p>Helping community members to solve small and big problems with their stores. Decluttering the admin UI with the removal of icons, cleaning up how currency is handled on orders.</p>
          <h6 class="text-gray-048">Fun fact</h6>
          <p>While waiting for the tests suite to pass he plays with his fingerskate.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bio-block">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md">
          <div class="card card-border-none">
            <div class="photo">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="<%= image_path('team/gregor-macdougall.png') %>" srcset="<%= image_path('team/gregor-macdougall.png') %>, <%= image_path('team/gregor-macdougall@2x.png') %> 2x" alt="Gregor MacDougall">
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="name">Gregor MacDougall</h3>
              <p>Engineering Lead <br> JUUL Labs</p>
              <ul class="links list-unstyled">
                <li>
                  <a href="https://github.com/gmacdougall" target="_blank"><%= inline_svg("social-icons/github.svg", class: "isvg") %> <strong>gmacdougall</strong></a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="data col-md">
          <h6 class="text-gray-048">Notable contribution</h6>
          <p>Pre-Solidus fork he spearheaded the initiative to enable Solidus to support multiple currencies. </p>
          <h6 class="text-gray-048">Fun fact</h6>
          <p>Gregor is an avid developer, theatre fan and board gamer.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bio-block">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md">
          <div class="card card-border-none">
            <div class="photo">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="<%= image_path('team/thomas-von-deyen.png') %>" srcset="<%= image_path('team/thomas-von-deyen.png') %>, <%= image_path('team/thomas-von-deyen@2x.png') %> 2x" alt="Thomas von Deyen">
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="name">Thomas von Deyen</h3>
              <p>Senior Web Developer <br> Core team member of AlchemyCMS</p>
              <ul class="links list-unstyled">
                <li>
                  <a href="https://github.com/tvdeyen" target="_blank"><%= inline_svg("social-icons/github.svg", class: "isvg") %> <strong>tvdeyen</strong></a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="data col-md">
          <h6 class="text-gray-048">Notable contribution</h6>
          <p>Doing a lot of Admin UI work. He’s passionate about good UI, I18n and understandable, well organized code.</p>
          <h6 class="text-gray-048">Fun fact</h6>
          <p>Bilingual, former hiphop DJ and producer, core team member of AlchemyCMS, and father of two.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bio-block">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md">
          <div class="card card-border-none">
            <div class="photo">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="<%= image_path('team/jacob-herrington.png') %>" srcset="<%= image_path('team/jacob-herrington.png') %>, <%= image_path('team/jacob-herrington@2x.png') %> 2x" alt="Jacob Herrington">
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="name">Jacob Herrington</h3>
              <p>Software Engineer <br> Engine</p>
              <ul class="links list-unstyled">
                <li>
                  <a href="https://github.com/jacobherrington" target="_blank"><%= inline_svg("social-icons/github.svg", class: "isvg") %> <strong>jacobherrington</strong></a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="data col-md">
          <h6 class="text-gray-048">Notable contribution</h6>
          <p>Investing in documentation and community. Jacob is interested in making Solidus absurdly developer-friendly.</p>
          <h6 class="text-gray-048">Fun fact</h6>
          <p>Jacob spends an unhealthy amount of time pursuing his disparate hobbies: video games, disc golf, podcasting, and most recently, bouldering.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bio-block">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md">
          <div class="card card-border-none">
            <div class="photo">
              <img class="img-fluid" src="<%= image_path('team/eric-saupe.png') %>" srcset="<%= image_path('team/eric-saupe.png') %>, <%= image_path('team/eric-saupe@2x.png') %> 2x" alt="Eric Saupe">
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="name">Eric Saupe</h3>
              <p>Senior Software Engineer <br> Deseret Book Company</p>
              <ul class="links list-unstyled">
                <li>
                  <a href="https://github.com/ericsaupe" target="_blank"><%= inline_svg("social-icons/github.svg", class: "isvg") %> <strong>ericsaupe</strong></a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="data col-md">
          <h6 class="subheading text-gray-048 text-uppercase">Notable contribution</h6>
          <p>Dedicated to making the out-of-the-box Solidus experience one that will put stores on a path to success.</p>
          <h6 class="subheading text-gray-048 text-uppercase">Fun fact</h6>
          <p>When he's not turning caffeine into code he's passionate about pandas, cookies, and his two young daughters.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

